  "description": "Deep antagonistic quality review of `hx-button-group` (T1-03). 4/6 libraries ship this.\n\nReview every file in `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-button-group/` critically.\n\n**Audit areas:**\n1. TypeScript — strict, slotted button typing, orientation prop typed\n2. Accessibility — `role=\"group\"` with accessible label, keyboard roving tabindex or sequential tab, connected borders don't affect focus visibility, axe-core pass\n3. Tests — horizontal/vertical orientation, mixed button types, disabled children, keyboard nav between buttons\n4. Storybook — orientation variants, mixed types demo\n5. CSS — shared borders between adjacent buttons, no gaps, `--hx-*` tokens, CSS parts\n6. Performance — bundle < 5KB\n7. Drupal — Twig-renderable with slotted buttons\n\n**Output:** Write findings to `packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-button-group/AUDIT.md` with severity (P0/P1/P2). DO NOT fix — document only. Commit AUDIT.md as your PR.",
